nodes.documentation:
@title CentralBank

* @dev @notice This contract allows :
              1. Central bank to issue or withdraw fund from settlement banks
              2. Transfer payment between authorized settlement banks
              3. Keep records for total issue fund and total refund(withdraw fund) for central bank
              4. View account balance for both central bank and settlement banks

* @author Cheryl Kwong
nodes.name: CentralBank
issueBank
withdrawBank
transferBank
getBalance

nodes.documentation:
@dev keep track of total fund being issued by central bank and withdraw back to central bank
@return total issued fund and total returned fund
nodes.name: getTotal

devdoc.details: @notice This contract allows :              1. Central bank to issue or withdraw fund from settlement banks              2. Transfer payment between authorized settlement banks              3. Keep records for total issue fund and total refund(withdraw fund) for central bank              4. View account balance for both central bank and settlement banks

addMobileNumber(uint256,address).details: Create mobile number account for client by settlement bank     Only settlement bank can perform this function

params.bank: the settlement bank which holds the mobile number account

addMobileRecord(uint256,address,uint256).details: Keep records of fund transfer between settlement banks for the mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function

allowance(address,address).details: Function to check the amount of tokens that an owner allowed to a spender.

params._owner: address The address which owns the funds.
params._spender: address The address which will spend the funds.

allowance(address,address).return: A uint256 specifying the amount of tokens still available for the spender.

approve(address,uint256).details: Approve the passed address to spend the specified amount of tokens on behalf of msg.sender.

params._spender: The address which will spend the funds.
params._value: The amount of tokens to be spent.

balanceOf(address).details: Gets the balance of the specified address.

params._owner: The address to query the the balance of.

balanceOf(address).return: An uint256 representing the amount owned by the passed address.

createBank(address,string).details: Create a new settlement bank account     Settlement bank role create

params.bankName: the name of the settlement bank

getBalance(address).details: get balance of a bank account

getBankDetails(address).return: bankName : the bank name of the search bankauthorization : indicate if the bank is active or close

getMobileNumberBanks(uint256).details: Retrieve the registered banks of mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function
getMobileNumberBanks(uint256).return: bank list belongs to mobile number

getMobileRecord(uint256).details: Retrieve records of fund transfer between settlement banks for the mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function

getTotal().details: keep track of total fund being issued by central bank and withdraw back to central bank
getTotal().return: total issued fund and total returned fund

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

issueBank(address,uint256).details: To issue fund to settlement bank account when it's created     Total amount of issued fund will be added

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: Called by a pauser to pause, triggers stopped state.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

removeBank(address).details: Remove a settlement bank account     Settlement bank role remove     Only contract Owner can perform this function

removeMobileNumber(uint256,address).details: Delete mobile number account for client by settlement bank     Only settlement bank can perform this function

params.bank: the settlement bank which holds the mobile number account

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

reopenBank(address).details: Reopen an closed settlement bank account     Settlement bank role added     Only contract Owner can perform this function

transfer(address,uint256).details: transfer token for a specified address

params.from: settlement account address of the payment sender

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Transfer tokens from one address to another

params._from: address The address which you want to send tokens from
params._to: address The address which you want to transfer to
params._value: uint256 the amount of tokens to be transferred

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: Called by a pauser to unpause, returns to normal state.

withdrawBank(address,uint256).details: To withdraw fund from a settlement account when bank closed     Total amount of withdraw fund wil be added
